snippet.title: Darza's Dominion - FINALLY!
snippet.description:
It's finally here, been wanting to make this video for ages now and only just figured out a way to record it without tremendous lag! 

Infinite's Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/user/KarateChieftain

Original Reddit post:
https://www.reddit.com/r/RotMG/comments/5taol9/darzas_dominion_the_mobile_rotmg_project_has_been/

Trailer:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sTYNpIe7bQk

Darza's official Wiki / website:
https://www.darzasdominion.com/wiki/



(for mobile users) IOS version:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/darzas-dominion/id1176328650?mt=8
(for mobile users) Android version:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.JuixGames.DarzasDominionNew
